title: GoStudent | Private Tutoring

creator: GoStudent GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Improve your child's school grades with GoStudent tutoring!

GoStudent matches every student with the ideal online tutor to boost your child's confidence and results. Why not download the GoStudent app and sign up for a free tutoring lesson today!

With GoStudent you can take online classes in math, trignonometry, algebra, English, physics, Spanish, biology, chemistry, and much more. GoStudent tutors are passionate about their subjects. We match students and tutors based on your child's learning needs, personality and interests to help keep your child motivated and excited to learn.

GoStudent private classes are suitable for students at elementary school, middle school, high school, college, and even adult learners.

How GoStudent tutoring works:
Step 1: Initial assessment
During the first call, we'll define the student's needs and choose the ideal tutor for them based on qualifications, personality and the student's requirements.

Step 2: Free trial lesson
The free trial lesson gives you the chance to get to know the tutor and discover how GoStudent works without any commitment. After the free trial, you can decide whether you want to sign up for a membership.

Step 3: Goal setting
In this phase, together with our educational advisors you'll define the student's goals and figure out the best way to achieve them together.

Step 4: Start learning
Once the membership starts you'll find everything you need on our platform. You can track progress, schedule or reschedule lessons, and more - all in just a few clicks.
Everything is included in one price

Examples of types of tutoring available
- Elementary school tutoring
- High school tutoring
- Long term academic support
- Homework help
- Exam prep
- Preparation for resits
- SSAT prep
- SAT prep
- ACT prep
- PSAT prep
- AP Prep
- High school diploma

Lesson organisation
- 100% flexible
- Easy scheduling
- 1:1 tutoring
- WhatsApp group with the tutor
- Automatic payment
- Substitute tutors guaranteed

Online learning
- Available on all devices
- Recording function
- Digital whiteboard
- Screen sharing
- Send and receive files

Additional features
- Referral programme
- Learning resources
- Progress updates
- Dedicated support team

Safe and secure with us
Our tutors all go through a rigorous selection process and only a comparatively small number is selected. This ensures that they have excellent subject knowledge and the right skills to help their students fulfil their potential.

With online classes, study and homework will no longer be a problem, even on weekends. Our tutors are available 7 days a week.

Do you need a help prepping for an important upcoming exam? Do you want to improve your grades? Do you want to learn programming or even a new language?
GoStudent tutors can help you achieve your goals! Download the app and sign up for a free tutoring lesson today!

title: GoStudent | Private Tutoring

creator: GoStudent GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Empower your child's learning journey with GoStudent, the ultimate online tutoring platform tailored to their unique needs. Download the app and claim a free trial lesson today!

GoStudent connects K-12 students with exceptional tutors for personalized online lessons in subjects like math, English, science, languages, and more. Our passionate tutors are carefully matched to your child's learning style, interests, and goals, ensuring a motivating and engaging learning experience.
Whether your child is in primary, secondary, or university level, or even an adult learner, GoStudent has the perfect tutor for them.

How GoStudent tutoring works:
1. Initial Assessment: We identify your child's needs and handpick the perfect tutor based on qualifications, personality, and requirements.
2. Free Trial Lesson: Experience our platform and meet your tutor with no commitment. Decide on a membership after the trial.
3. Goal Setting: Collaborate with our educational advisors to set achievable goals and plan the best path to success.
4. Start Learning: Access our platform to track progress, schedule lessons, and more - all with just a few clicks.

Tutoring options include:
- Primary & Secondary School Support
- Long-term Academic Guidance
- Homework Assistance
- Exam Preparation & Revision
- Resits & Specialized Exam Tutoring (GCSE, A Level, 11+, SAT, Scottish Higher, National 5)

Flexible & Convenient:
- Easy Scheduling & Rescheduling
- 1:1 Tutoring Sessions
- WhatsApp Group with Tutor
- Automatic Payments
- Guaranteed Substitute Tutors

Innovative Online Learning:
- Accessible on All Devices
- Lesson Recording Function
